OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FA survivor of the Medomsley Detention
OL,8,FCentre abuse scandal says he hopes the
OL,9,Fbeginning of a fresh investigation
OL,10,Finto what happened will allow "the
OL,11,Ftruth" to come out.
OL,13,FEric Sampson, who has waived his right
OL,14,Fto anonymity, was 17 when he was sent
OL,15,Fto Medomsley near , County Durham, in
OL,16,Fthe 1970s.
OL,18,FHe is one of around 2,000 young men
OL,19,Fand boys to come forward with
OL,20,Fallegations of physical and sexual
OL,21,Fabuse while interned at the facility.
