OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSeveral former officers have been
OL,8,Fconvicted for their actions at the
OL,9,Ffacility following an extensive
OL,10,Fcriminal investigation by Durham
OL,11,FConstabulary, called Operation
OL,12,FSeabrook, which ended in 2023.
OL,14,FNow, the Prisons and Probation
OL,15,FOmbudsman (PPO) has launched its own
OL,16,Findependent inquiry into what happened
OL,17,Fat the centre and why it was allowed
OL,18,Fto continue for so long.
