OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe development has been welcomed by
OL,8,FMr Sampson who is hopeful that it will
OL,9,Fallow more information about what
OL,10,Fhappened to come out.
OL,12,F"I think a lot more people will come
OL,13,Fforward," he told ITV Tyne Tees. "The
OL,14,Ftruth needs to come out about what was
OL,15,Fgoing on in these places.
OL,17,F"I think it has a good chance of
OL,18,Ffinding out a lot more information
OL,19,Fabout what actually went on in there.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
