OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"A lot of people are too scared to
OL,8,Fcome forward now because they are
OL,9,Fmarried with families and that. But I
OL,10,Fadvise anybody now to come forward
OL,11,Fwith what they know about the place.
OL,12,FCome forward and tell the story.
OL,14,F"The officers as well who are still
OL,15,Falive and worked in there. They must
OL,16,Fcome forward now and tell the truth."
