OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"I know a few other people's lives its
OL,8,Fruined but what can you do? Some lads
OL,9,Fhave picked up the pieces and been
OL,10,Fmarried and that but I don't suppose
OL,11,Fthat is a lot of them."
OL,13,FThe PPO investigation is still in its
OL,14,Fvery early stages, but some of the
OL,15,Fevidence has already had a
OL,16,Fconsiderable impact on the
OL,17,Finvestigating officers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
