OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"All of us have been touched on a
OL,8,Fhuman level," Ombudsman, Adrian Usher,
OL,9,Fexplained. "I don't think it is too
OL,10,Fmuch for us to admit that some sleep
OL,11,Fhas been lost from what we have seen
OL,12,Feven now when we are in the very
OL,13,Fnascent stage of the investigation.
OL,15,F"What happened to those men and in
OL,16,Fsome cases those children is some of
OL,17,Fthe most appalling sexual and physical
OL,18,Fabuse I have ever come across and on a
OL,19,Fscale, I have never come across."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
