OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe investigation has been
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Justice Secretary,
OL,9,Fbut it will work independently of the
OL,10,Fgovernment, police and the prison
OL,11,Fservice.
OL,13,FThe nature of the inquiry has been
OL,14,Falso been welcomed by lawyers
OL,15,Frepresenting victims of the scandal
OL,16,Fwith hopes the evidence collected will
OL,17,Fstrengthen the case for a wider public
OL,18,Finquiry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
