OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FDavid Greenwood, solicitor at
OL,8,FSwitalskis said: "I believe more
OL,9,Fofficers are likely to emerge from
OL,10,Fthis kind of investigation and there
OL,11,Fmight be referrals to the crown
OL,12,Fprosecution service when the evidence
OL,13,Fcomes out.
OL,15,F"The ideal is a judge-led independent
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry, that's what we asked
OL,17,Ffor in the first place.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
